
At the moment these are the list of things to do in the CHB project.

For bug tracking, please write to:

	https://github.com/Andres2626/CHB-Bootloader/issues
	
or

	andrescamorao9@gmail.com
    
                          * Andres26 *

==========================================================================

- Support for mounted disks in FAT driver
- Add support for other filesystems like ext2, exfat, FAT32, ...
- Disk and CDROM support (INT13,4X)
- Executable formats (pe, coff, a.out, ...)
- Implement UEFI
- Non x86 support (arm, mips, ...)
- Multiboot specification
- Long mode support
- VFS support
- Memory map
- Rework floppy controller in stage1
- Report disk geometry in stage1 (INT13,8)
- Create documentation
- Implement Command line
